                              'Korners' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Korners' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to place
'Korners', which are 90 degrees angle tiles, so they make square
shapes. Squares are made with four types of 'Korners': an upper
left Korner, an upper right Korner, a lower left and a lower
right Korner. A full square occupies a 2 by 2 space area...

  The more Korners of the same type there are in each completed
square, the more points you get...

  Have fun!

